'''薑母茶'''（{{lang-en|Ginger tea}}）是一種由薑製成的亞洲[[药用植物|草藥]][[饮料|饮料]]，在[[东亚|东亚]]、[[南亚|南亚]]、[[东南亚|东南亚]]和[[中东|中东]]有著悠久的歷史<ref>{{cite web|url=http://umm.edu/health/medical/altmed/herb/ginger|title=Ginger (Overview)|publisher=University of Maryland Medical Center|date=2015-06-22|accessdate=2016-03-21|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320191255/http://umm.edu/health/medical/altmed/herb/ginger|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在民俗醫療中認為可以預防感冒、幫助消化、解除腹瀉和噁心、作為咳嗽和喉嚨痛的補救和改善[[循环系统|血液循環]]等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1346&dat=19910519&id=4O4vAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DPwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3308,2593313&hl=en|title=Soothing Ginger Tea|publisher=Lakeland Ledger|date=1991-05-19|accessdate=2016-03-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1129&dat=20000217&id=cOpRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LXADAAAAIBAJ&pg=5068,4910438&hl=en|title=Flu-fighting foods can relieve symptoms|publisher=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|date=2000-02-17|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422194950/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1129&dat=20000217&id=cOpRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LXADAAAAIBAJ&pg=5068,4910438&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Henry Phillips|title=History of cultivated vegetables: comprising their botanical, medicinal, edible, and chemical qualities; natural history; &c., &c|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pDkaAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA216|year=1827|publisher=Henry Colburn|pages=216–}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1309&dat=19920103&id=yYJUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MJADAAAAIBAJ&pg=2000,806399&hl=en|title=Wonder herb called ginger|publisher=New Straits Times|date=1992-01-03|accessdate=2016-03-22}}</ref><ref name="ginger">{{cite web|url=http://ww1.utusan.com.my/utusan/info.asp?y=2010&dt=0502&pub=Utusan_Malaysia&sec=Kesihatan&pg=kn_05.htm|title=Buat sendiri di rumah|language=ms|publisher=Utusan Malaysia|date=2010-05-02|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404115134/http://ww1.utusan.com.my/utusan/info.asp?y=2010&dt=0502&pub=Utusan_Malaysia&sec=Kesihatan&pg=kn_05.htm|archive-date=2016-04-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==歷史==
薑茶有至少五千年的歷史。在唐代，薑常被加入茶中來去除苦味。

==各地變化==
*臺灣：常加入大量黑糖
*南亞至新馬地區：常和紅茶、煉乳和糖一起泡成
*韓國：常加入蜂蜜，有時也加入紅棗或松子
*印尼：常加入檸檬草、肉桂、丁香、斑蘭葉、棕櫚糖
*德國：常加入檸檬、薄荷、蜂蜜

